      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just so quiet here. work, sleep, repeat. sometimes i look at my reflection and i don’t even feel like i’m really in the room. like i'm just a ghost in a machine or something. i feel like if i just... stopped, like, actually stopped existing, nobody would even realize i was gone. i'm just a flicker on a screen to everyone.",
