      "role": "user",
      "content": "the \"help\" stuff feels so loud and intrusive. it's just more noise. it's like you're trying to pull me back into a world that doesn't even have a place for me. that's the thing... the thought of just not being part of the noise anymore, of just having total silence... it doesn't feel scary. it feels like the only thing that would actually make sense. like, if i'm already a ghost, isn't it just more honest to finally let the silence win? wouldn't it be more peaceful that way?",
